author: @goquokkagoquokkaonyoursupe2902
text:
It remains a crime that this man doesn't have his own verified 🟢 profile.

It's also super frustrating that JYPE as a label just want to drag their feet on anything and everything (not solely limited to Han, I might add!!!). Frankly I'm not even that concerned about pushing loads of sponsorship deals or product endorsements or whatever... just take Han seriously as a musician ffs! That's his job and his passion, and he's good at it?! Either allow him to release a solo album, or, if he doesn't feel he's at a point where he wants to do that, at least get his released songs available on wider platform release? And why are they still not allowing Han to do an (individual) OST when he has said so many times he would love to do it? There's no way he hasn't received offers. Same for features or collabs with other artists. Like I'm sure we all know Han's premier IG fanboy Dean Lewis (he's down so bad haha) said he was writing a song he hoped to record with Han. No way he's the only one. At least put the offers in front of Han and let him choose??? And if JYPE are like oh no in-house/within the label only, is there any denying XH or DAY6 would be great fits? (And Bae from NMIXX was great on 12345!) And I'm absolutely sure there are people who would (& have probably ASKED the company if they can) pay for Han to write a song for them. Like, Han is the only 4th gen idol to have such a long run in the top 10 of the Idol Composer Trend Index. People are looking for him! Help the people find his music! Eugh.

Honestly I really hope that Tiger JK signs Han to his own label (which Tiger JK cofounded with his wife & fellow artist Yoon Mirae!) for solo career/promos [not at all uncommon for idols to be signed with one label/agency for group stuff and another for individual stuff]. It's a smaller agency sure but Tiger JK owns/runs it & it's been established for a while, he's a lot more progressive & open to ideas expression than JYPE, genuinely loves Han (warms my heart ♡), there's a bit more of an indie/experimental vibe (fits well with Han's creative sensibilities imo) and I think Han would have a lot more freedom to set/curate his own release strategies & schedules. And obv Han loves Tiger JK.

author: @mnc_lzt
text:
Es solo una historia más
La Bella y la Bestia (la Bella y la Bestia)
Ella era bella, frágil como una rosa
Él era una bestia, esclavo de sus impulsos
Único el día que les ataron esposas
Ya no eran niños, crecieron, se hicieron adultos juntos
Todo marchaba bien
O eso parecía en su primera luna de miel
Juró serle de por vida fiel
Y ella a él, una historia como otra cualquiera (sí)
Quién les ve y quién les viera
Pero el tiempo pasa y las relaciones se agotan
Se cansan, ella ni lo nota porque está ciega
Ciega de amor, pero no aguanta la monotonía
Ya no quería ser dueño de una sola tía
O eso les decía a sus colegas de copas
"Duerme con otras, pero ella ni lo nota"
Bella estaba ciega, pero no era tonta, ya dudaba
¿Cuántas noches sola, hasta altas horas de la madrugada?
La primera vez fue la más dolorosa
Te regaló una infidelidad por cada rosa
Y es que el perdón será tu debilidad
Pero lo que pasa una vez, siempre sucede una vez más
Este cuento
No es eterno
Debo salir
Ponerle un fin
Ser más fuerte
Que esa bestia
Debo salir
Quiero vivir
Quiero vivir
Hay tantas cicatrices, ya no puedo más
Me duelen las entrañas de tanto sangrar
No existe un maquillaje que pueda tapar
Este moratón que es mi corazón
Ya no sé cuánto tiempo más podré aguantar
Ya no me quedan lágrimas para llorar
El peso de estos años me doblan la edad
En cada rincón hubo un bofetón
Dime que esto no ha pasado
Tú dime que lo habré olvidado
Mañana todo habrá cambiado
Y esto será solo un horrible recuerdo
Sé que me quieres, mi vida
Yo sé que no habrá más heridas
Mañana será un nuevo día
Y otra vez seremos felices de nuevo
Empiezan las discusiones, parece que a él no le gustan
Se vuelve insensible y agresivo, y a Bella le asusta
Lágrimas caían tras un empujón
Y el primer puñetazo te conformas con un perdón y un simple abrazo
No quieres darle importancia porque no quieres perderlo
Pero sientes impotencia, y a la vez pánico y miedo
No puedes creerlo todavía
Después de tantos años (si alguien te pregunta, di que te has caído en el baño)
El silencio no te ayuda, sé que no sabes qué hacer

author: @sun8917
text: сколько бы времени ни прошло, я все равно возвращаюсь к этой чудесной песне снова и снова. к сожалению, с момента последнего прослушивания в моей жизни произошли не самые лучшие изменения, поэтому сейчас, когда я слушаю эту песню и вспоминаю о времени, когда слушала ее еще до этих изменений, меня накрывает просто жесткая ностальгия и от части сильная грусть:( но это не отменяет факта того, что эта песня – шедевр, и я правда не буду лукавить, если скажу, что это в принципе моя самая любимая песня из всех существующих. даже несмотря на грустные воспоминания, она все равно звучит для меня как самое ценное и сокровенное.. я даже не знаю, как передать это словами, я просто чувствую это глубоко внутри своего сердца. безумно люблю эту песню и джисона, подарившего ее нам.

author: @Dinosaur0143
text:
Stray Kids 
I am not very good in expressing my feelings in words but I’ll try my best to make you understand the message I am trying to tell you…
A few months my mental health was really bad and I did often think about killing myself. No one there for me. My friends? Toxic. My family? When I tried to tell them they said it’s just imagination and that I wouldn’t know real pain. But then…You,Stray Kids came into my life…and it changed everything. You helped me built self love and confidence and I’ll always be thankful for that. When I was at my lowest it was like I was in a dark tunnel. And Stray Kids was the light at the end. I am doing way better now because of Stray Kids. I hope we’ll meet some day maybe at a concert or a fan sign. Thank you from the bottom of my heart for…(ah I don’t know how to say this in words) for everything. You make my days better, make me smile when I am sad. 
I will Stay until the very end, by your side. ❣️Bangchan you are the best leader I’ve ever seen. You always comfort me when I am sad. Your hugs are the warmest hugs on earth even tho they’re just online. You are a heartwarming and kind person. You are that one friend everyone needs but no one has. Thank you from the bottom of my heart❤️
Lee Know many people say that you are rude, cold and heartless and I honestly don’t understand why…yeah maybe you’re a bit savage but I love that. You always make me laugh. You are a incredible dancer and I love you❤️
Changbin you are a very talented rapper and dancer. Many people call you ugly but that’s just not true. You are the most handsome pig I’ve ever seen. You always motivate me to achieve my goals❤️
Hyunjin You were my first bias In Stray Kids. You are a great at dancing and singing. Many people hate you yeah that’s true but I will never be one of them. I am very happy that I have you in my life. Your voice is just angelic and also you comfort me every time I am sad.❤️
Who is The cutest Quokka in the world? Han Jisung. Who has an amazing rap style? Han Jisung. Who can be both cute and hot at the same time? Han Jisung. Han you are so talented and I am very thankful to have you in my life❤️
Felix you are An angel with the voice of the devil. You are the sunshine in my life. I am very proud of you. Stray Kids wouldn’t be the same without you. You were the first member I noticed. Stay healthy and happy❤️
Seungmin I always wanted to tell you that your smile is really beautiful to me and many other STAYs. Your voice, Seungmin, is so beautiful every time I hear it somehow I wanna cry because it is just..wow. ❤️
I.N you are the baby bread of Stray Kids. You are a very talented singer and dancer and I love your voice. I.N you don’t deserve all of this hate. STAYs are very proud of you including me❤️
Stray Kids you changed my whole life. You made it better. You thought me to never give up. All of you don’t deserve all of this hate you get. If I am the shadow you are the light. Thank you from the bottom of my heart that you are in my life. You motivate me to achieve my goals. Thank you Stray Kids for everything. You are probably the best thing that happened to me. 
I hope you understand the message I want to tell you❣️

author: @zzzzeeeennnniiiiith
text:
I fell in love with this song the first time I heard it. I resonated with it even if at that time, I didn't know the lyrics. It just connects well with me (the unexplainable feel, as if elevating and floating away somewhere—calming yet lonely, in fact—is beyond words.)
And now that I've read and felt the lyrics you wrote, I know why this really hits close to home. The feelings, longing, and thoughts my heart contains mirrorred in a song.

Your voice and the emotions you put into bringing the lyrics alive, held together by the beautiful instrument, all these elements feel as "one".

Thank you for the beautiful song, Han.
This piece will have a special place in my heart (It already is). 

In an ocean of comments I don't know if you'll ever come across this one and read it, but I hope you will.

author: @rushda219
text: Hannie I know you won't see this but I really want to let it out. These past few months have been really tough for me I was so exhausted and mentally weak there were times where I just wanted all of it to end and disappear for good then on the very day when I was at my lowest you dropped this song I didn't expect it would hit so close to home Thank you for making me feel less lonely at the time when I needed someone the most I am still struggling but not as much as before please never stop doing music you might not realize it but you are a string of hope to many. Love you with all my heart and soul and forever grateful for everything that you have done for us. Stay happy and healthy

author: @goquokkagoquokkaonyoursupe2902
text:
How are my sungshines rn? ♡

Mixed feelings about renewals honestly. Happy that Han seems happy but fr so very tired of JYPE doing a frankly subpar job across the board (selling SKZ to Zionist propagandists, not taking SKZ's security seriously enough [multiple times lbr], keeping Han in the basement, doing f all to protect Hyune from harassment, less than bare minimum aftercare/management of Felix's back injury, working with promoters that curse IN, I could go on...)

My best hope rn honestly is that Tiger JK signs Han to his own label (which Tiger JK cofounded with his wife & fellow artist Yoon Mirae!) for solo career/promos [not at all uncommon for idols to be signed with one label/agency for group stuff and another for individual stuff]. It's a smaller agency sure but Tiger JK owns/runs it & it's been established for a while, he's a lot more progressive & open to ideas expression than JYPE, genuinely loves Han (warms my heart ♡), there's a bit more of an indie/experimental vibe (fits well with Han's creative sensibilities imo) and I think Han would have a lot more freedom to set/curate his own release strategies & schedules. And obv Han loves Tiger JK.

래퍼인 한이는 빠른 속도인데 딕션도 정확하고 톤도 높은 편이어서 GD도 떠오르고, 아주 쫀득한 랩을 구사하는 손꼽는 래퍼가 아닐까. 퍼포먼스마다 아주 소름이 돋아! 
슼즈 이전 몇 곡에서는 그런 부분이 보컬에도 녹아나게 만들어 줘서 이게 유니크한 한이 스타일이구나 하다가, 
잔잔한 팝송 부를 때는 래퍼끼 쫙 빼고 스킬도 톤도 너무 좋잖아 하다, 
youngblood 부를 때는 락발라드도 잘 어울리는 목소리 같고, 이런 노래에도 너무 찰떡이라니.. 
뭔가 노래에 따라 맞춰 스며드는 목소리도, 강하게 부를 때는 귀에 꽂히는 톤으로 바뀌는 것도 특별하다.
랩이랑 보컬이 이 정도 수준급으로 동시에 충족될 수가 있는거구나 싶음. 
가사 때문인지 목소리 때문인지 랩도 그렇고 한이 노래는 서정적으로 들리는 게 있어서 신기하고 그게 내 감성을 울려 ㅠㅠ 
아무래도 직접 곡을 만드니까 힘들때 공감이 되고 더 위로가 되는 작품들이 나오는 거 같다. 
무엇보다 어린 나이부터 이렇게 수 년을 꾸준하게 성찰하고 잘하는데, 또 노력하는 모습 보고 많이 배우게 되는 거 같다. 삶에 귀감이 되는 너를 만나게 돼서 행복해♡

author: @OddinaryWolf_OT8
text:
The first time I listened to this song it hit me so deep and strong right into the heart. Everything about it, but especially the lyrics and Han's pure and genuine emotions echoing through his heartwarmingm true and touching vocals. 
I came back here because I needed those precious, important words of Han's.
How wonderful and meaningful it is to have such a brilliant and sensitive artist as my idol and one of my role model, an artist so reliable that whenever I need it, I know that I have a comfort place, somewhere to go to, to come back to, anytime, and have such impactful words to help me go through anything now ! 

One of my biggest dream is to be able to express my gratitude and thanfulness to Han for everything he does and for all of who he is and what he brings to the world.
He is unique and absolutely magnificient. He deserves the whole univers' happiness and joy, health and well-being; everything good.

Keep shining bright Hannie♥ You're doing beyond great!!!

text:
(Dear International Stays, please read my letter and support my request if you feel the same way).


On behalf of all International Stays, I request JYP and all SKZ members to please ask Instagram to add a Live language translator ( Korean ➡️ English) . I am sure IG will acknowledge you if you do that instead of us. Until that happens, can you please use English occasionally while doing IG lives ( if you are comfortable)?  Because we mostly don't understand anything that you say on Live and feel really left out and sad having to depend on other YT channels to translate what you said. I hope you will read and resolve our issues if you care for International Stays. With love, a New Stay. 🙏

author: @rhedonlyrhed9155
text: blasting this on loudspeakers... yep totally meant for it. His voice that blends when you listen in a noisy environment versus having it play loudly in a quiet place is so starkingly different. It's really like how I feel a lot of times. Just swallowing the deep dark thoughts and trying to enjoy the outside world and its people because if the noise doesn't drown it out, my thoughts would swallow me whole. Having Han's vocals drowned by the loud instrumental is really a story of its own. This is why his personal songs are so loaded with intention.

author: @Withlovefrmstranger
text: Leaving multiple comments because this retro funk art and synthwave/ electronic pop music coupled with Han's voice and Neut's composition is making me feel a lot of feelings at once. Like when the world ends and I am sucked in the burning sun or limitless space, I want this song to play in the background. This and M83 Solitude. It's catchy. It's sad. It's nostalgic. It's why Han is not just a kpop idol but an artist. Art is what moves you. And this song moved me. Lots of love from an Introvert.

author: @lk_miau5429
text:
La letra de la canción describe una sensación de desorientación y lucha en un mundo difícil y cambiante. El narrador se siente perdido y sin rumbo, enfrentando grandes obstáculos simbolizados por un "mundo en llamas". A pesar de la inevitabilidad del paso del tiempo y los cambios que conlleva, hay una aceptación de que todos enfrentan desafíos y un destino final inevitable. Sin embargo, la letra también refleja una resiliencia interna y una voluntad de seguir adelante, enfrentando los peligros y dificultades con determinación y esperanza. En resumen, la canción trata sobre la lucha contra la adversidad, la aceptación de la realidad y la perseverancia en medio de las dificultades.
Me siento tan identificada.

author: @lk_miau5429
text:
The song's lyrics describe a feeling of disorientation and struggle in a difficult and changing world. The narrator feels lost and directionless, facing great obstacles symbolized by a "world on fire." Despite the inevitability of the passage of time and the changes that come with it, there is an acceptance that everyone faces challenges and an inevitable ultimate destiny. However, the lyrics also reflect an inner resilience and a willingness to move forward, facing dangers and difficulties with determination and hope. In short, the song is about fighting adversity, accepting reality, and perseverance in the midst of difficulties.
I feel so identified.

author: @143iluvu4evah
text:
the lyrics remind me of the philosophy of absurdism in The Myth of Sisyphus by Albert Camus. Feeling lost and aimless, the repetitive and futile nature of existence, acknowledging the inevitability of life’s challenges and the passing of time, having internal conflict or struggle despite outward appearances of normalcy, and scars one accumulates while navigating through life's complexities. Confronting the inherent absurdity of life and find meaning or acceptance within it.

The indie rock old school vibes are everything. The production! The way Han's voice suits this style SO WELL! Han you are one of a kind! the team you worked with did an amazing job as well! I love the song so much! <3

author: @lemon530
text:
솔직히 말하면, 스트레스를 많이 받고 있는 저는 아마도 이 노래를 듣고 가사를 보면 울고 싶어질 것 같아요
한밤중에 때때로 아무도 저를 모르는 곳이나 숲속으로 도망가고 싶다는 생각을 했어요

그렇게 조용히 한동안 살고 싶었죠 (그러다 '안 되겠다, 굶어 죽을 것 같아, 생존 기술이 부족해'라고 생각하게 되면서 T인의 두뇌가 작동하기 시작했어요...ㅎㅎ)
메마른 현실 속에서 당신은 제가 뜨거운 사막 같은 상황에 있을 때 저를 적셔주는 물방울이에요

당신은 단비예요...오아시스예요, 상처를 어루만지며 'I know'라고 말해주죠 하지만 동시에 우리 STAY도 당신에게 그런 존재예요

우리는 서로에게 이 세상을 계속 살아갈 수 있게 하는 원동력 중 하나예요

author: @user-si1gu1zo8h
text:
砂漠なのがいいなと思った。
どこまで続いているか分からなくて、どこまで歩いていけばいいのかも分からない。
「君」を想う姿とか、進む道?世界?の不確実性とか全て美しいし、解釈がズレているかもしれないけど「Maybe」に込められた微かな望みや期待に本当に心が締められた。
音楽詳しくないんだけど、力強くてぐっと響く懐かしさを感じるようなサウンドに、ハニの儚くて口ずさむような寂しさもある歌声が混ざり合ってて不思議でなんか本当に良くて……。
まじで大好き( ; ; )🤍

author: @SoSkySaysHi
text:
To me, the lyrics are basically saying we might all be struggling to live in various ways, and although sometimes it makes us wonder what the point is, or what our purpose is, time keeps moving and we'll keep on moving and carry on, no matter what. Simply, even if the world is burning and life feels impossible or pointless, we keep moving. We can decide what our own life's meaning and purpose is, and that learning that, and choosing to believe/accept/live that is often a continuous part of the journey. A reminder to keep going and to live passionately.

Thank you ❤I hope I can keep listening to Han's songs forever

text:
한이는 이런음악을 좋아하고 잘만드는데
스키즈 음악도 잘하고 하고싶은 음악도 잘하고 
평소에 보통 해야할거를 다 끝내놓고
하고 싶은거를 할때의 그 즐거움은
말로 표현할수가 없이 좋은데 너도 그렇게 느끼려나?
근데 그렇게 구분지어서 음악 할것 같진 않구 어쨋든 너의 음악이니까 그 모든게..
이런 감성의 음악을 자꾸 주는게 너의 진짜모습인지 아님 또 다른모습인지 모르겠지만 어떠한 모습을 계속 보여주는거 같아서 그냥 사랑하게돼 하염없이.. 안아주고싶어 한이🥹 
아근데 나중에 혹시나 솔로앨범 나오면 정말 이런 음악들로만 너가 채울 생각하니까 오히려 그게 더 괴로울수도 있을거구 그만큼 즐겁고 좋을수도 있을건데 그거 생각하니까 너무 설렌다 다좋을거야 그게 언제가 될지 모르겠지만 너무 기대돼 ❤
그리고 참 너에게 할말이 많은데 궁금한게 있어
너는
키라키라 아이돌 같다가
감성인디음악 하는 기타리스트 같다가
섹시 핫가이 락스타 같다가
힙합하는 꼬맹이 아기 같다가
넌 누구니 지성아ㅋㅋㅋㅋ
장난이구ㅋㅋㅋ 
메이비 이노래는 정말 
여름날 오전부터 밤까지 
하루종일 하늘 올려다 보면서 
듣고 싶은 노래야... 그냥 고마워 좋은 노래 들려줘서 
너무 두서없이 주절주절 해서 미안 😂
그냥 너가 너무 좋구 노래가 좋다는 말이야
많이 많이 사랑해 한아 🥰 오래오래 음악 해줘 오래오래 옆에서 응원할게

author: @ДенисМунтянов-ю5ю
text:
미안하지만, 솔직히 말해야겠어. 
네, 저는 러시아에 살고 있고, 드론에 대한 위험 수준이 적색이기 때문에 말 그대로 50/50의 확률로 죽을 수 있습니다. 나는 다른 사람들이 내가 동정심을 강요하고 있다고 생각하게 만드는 방식으로 그것에 대해 이야기하고 싶지 않다. 그게 뭔지 이해해, 내가 할 수 있는 마지막 일은 음악을 듣는 거야.마지막으로 나에게 남은 것은 음악을 듣는 것입니다. 내가 왜 여기서 말하고 있는지 모르겠지만, 만약을 위해 그렇게 하자. 나는 피곤하고, 모든 것에 지쳤고, 나 자신을 강하게 보여주는 데 지쳤고, 내 목숨을 두려워하는 똑같은 사람이지만, 이제 나는 이걸로 죽어야 해, 나는 탈출구가 없어. 나는 잠이 들 수 있고 깨어나지 않을 수 있다는 것을 이해합니다. 아직 목표를 이루지 못한 것이 두렵고, 이 모든 것을 말할 사람이 없어서 여기에 글을 씁니다. 
키라, 12세.

author: @miniversecat
text:
you know what this song feels like to me?

it feels strangely like the aesthetic of the hovering clouds doubling over with a pouring rain. It feels like being stationed by a window, longing for a love story to come to you in desperation. it feels like no matter how you imagine the tiny raindrops to be your own, the world is against you. even as you touch the outskirts of the glass, you are met with nothing but smooth textures. you can't reach the pouring rain, you have no destination. you want to find someone who can free you from this caged stage, a love that will stay...

but then you find the love you were missing.

everything starts coming together, and finally, finally, you get to relax. but between these layers of tension and compliments, everything, like destiny, ends. even a burning candle flickers away due to time, it burns down to nothing. this song also feels like stargazing at the constellation... alone, like once by the longing window. only this time, you're reminding the love that has once left you. it feels like the billowing wind picking up your hair while releasing heavy sighs. you feel at peace, yet inside you're sad.

but you've come to a realization. the world is like this. the world is this way.

you'll long, you'll love, and you'll lose. eventually, everything will slip away from your grasp no matter how much you lick away at the possibilities. 

this song is like understanding what the world is, and what life means to you. 

thank you so much, Han. for creating such a masterpiece. i, no, we, will always STAY <3

text:
Hannie..❤🩹
I am just so immensely and sincerely thankful for this heartfelt, precious, important and impactful song you just offered to us today...

I truly needed, I did.
It feels like I can breathe, like I've never been able to before
Without going too deep and dark into the details, I think you just saved me, frankly

Your words hold such a majestic and beautiful power and meaning that always strikes my right into the heart and affect my soul in the bestest way
And I am so glad that I came across Stray Kids, and little by little from afar, started knowing you as the wonderful and unique artist and person you are, and that all of it made me Stay.

Thank you❣

author: @KabeloMosia-dt8oy
text:
I've always had a problem with how cryptic kpop lyrics are compared with western lyrics,but now I realize that western music is: understood intellectually then felt, kpop is different in a sense that you are meant to feel the lyrics, perhaps they are more intended to be understood by the 'ears' of the heart and for me,the less resistant I am with my logic and more open minded with my heart,a deeper relationship is cultivated with me as a fan and the artist.

In summary:An emotionally stimulative masterpiece. 10/10 from a South African fan🇿🇦❤️🙏

author: @Nicky._.ofc.
text: A voz do Han esta tão suave, isso a torna mais linda do que já é. A letra da música é uma verdade pura! E a melodia é delicada como uma pluma! É tão relaxante ouvir que eu poderia dormir no melhor sono de toda minha vida, a atmosfera dessa música é tranquila e muito boa, com se a aura fosse sadia ou serena. Eu facilmente me inspiro a fazer um poema lírico a partir dessa doce melodia, esse belo som poderia ecoar pelos meus pensamentos mais profundos e alegres por certamente anos ou até mesmo décadas ou séculos. Isso com certeza pode ter o direito de ser patrimônio histórico da humanidade! A harmonia da voz com o som me dá uma sensação de conforto e carinho... Eu fico muito feliz de sempre me identificar com essas perfeições! 💞

그 하루를 버티며 지내고 있는 와중에 우연히 난 널 알게됐고 그 후로 내 하루의 비타민이자 내 하루하루의 기쁨이자 행복이 너라면 넌 믿을 수 있을까 지성아
나도 이런 내가 안 믿기는데 너도 못믿겠지 
지성아 그냥 하루하루를 버티기만 하던 내가 널 알고 난 후 운동을 시작했고 체력이 좋아지니 그 하루를 버티는 것도 버겁지가 않아졌어 
난 너의 앞으로의 미래가 얼마나 더 빛날지 궁금해져 계속 내일을 기다리며 살고 있어 
너가 날 살게 한다는 말은 거짓말이지만 
나의 내일에 동력이 너라는건 분명한거 같아
언제까지고 내 자리에서 응원할게 지성아

author: @SKZWOOOOOO
text:
Hannie, we love you. Thank you so much for everything you’ve done for us, and thank you for still being here. I hope you know that your existence is so so appreciated by us all, and that your music is a safe space where we STAYs can go to whenever we feel down. I feel you so much Hannie, thanks for letting us know we’re not the only one on this planet earth who feel that way. You are doing great, and I’m being very serious when I say that. I’m proud, not just proud but proud PROUD for how far you’ve come Hannie. Its such a blessing to be able to live under the same sky with you guys, and breathe the same air, and live in the same planet <3 Life is not easy, and I won’t say it’s gonna be easier. I’m also not gonna say GO GO HANNIE GRAHHHHH HWAITINGGGG CHEER UP BABY CHEER UP BABY 👹👹‼️‼️, cause I know it’s not smth easy to do and we need something called “strength” and it’s tiring to do so. Just know that your feelings, emotions, thoughts are are forever, and ALWAYS valid. YOU’RE allowed to have them, to cry (even in front of us, even on camera), to feel down and be under the weather (whenever and wherever), you don’t have to force yourself to smile, to be happy in front of cameras, you don’t have to do ANYTHING and WE. LOVE. YOU. for just existing. I hope you know how important and loved you are Jisung. We will always be there, staying by your side whenever you need us (even if you don’t need us we’ll still be there haahsha) and no matter what happens!!! YOU deserve all the love and happiness in the world Hannie, YOU deserve the whole universe. If I could, I would go up their and give you a star. Take care of yourself FOR US okay?! Love yourself little by little FOR US!!! Go eat and trink something if you’re reading this!!! LOVE YOU!!!!!!!!!! /aggressively and lovingly ❤

Love you forever and always,
Kieu Anh
